# Blur It
This package is aimed to build to blur different portions of a image. Currently it blurs eyes in human photograph.

[![PyPI version](https://badge.fury.io/py/blurit.svg)](https://badge.fury.io/py/blurit)

## Install
```sh
pip install blurit
```

## Usage
```sh
from py-blur import blur_eyes_in_images   
#call the below function to blur eye in a image
blur_eyes_in_images(file_base_path,save_base_path,size)
#file_base_path -  path of the folder that contains images
#save_base_path - path of the images generated
#size - height and width of the blur
```



